---
const features = [
  {
    id: '1',
    name: 'Research and Discovery',
    description:
    `To craft a truly impactful design, it's crucial for me to grasp both the user's challenges and your business objectives. This means diving deep into user research—I'll engage with users through conversations, conduct surveys, and perform usability tests, essentially channeling my inner Sherlock Holmes to unearth insights. Beyond understanding our users, I'll scope out the competition and the broader market landscape, drawing inspiration and strategically borrowing brilliant ideas. Armed with a comprehensive understanding, I'll pinpoint the core problem and unleash my creativity, brainstorming solutions with the zeal of a mad scientist ready to innovate.`    
  },
  {
    id: '2',
    name: 'Design and Prototyping',
    description:
    `I'll start by diving into the creative process with low-fidelity sketches and wireframes, sparking the initial flow of design ideas. Then, I'll enter a phase of refinement, iterating on these concepts with input from our team, users, and my network of design experts. Once we've honed in on the best ideas, it's time to elevate our game with high-fidelity mockups, bringing the designs to life with stunning detail and soliciting further feedback.

The next step is prototyping—where I take charge, transforming our concepts into interactive experiences to test and validate our ideas with real users. Following this, I'll develop a comprehensive design system, ensuring visual consistency across all touchpoints and facilitating seamless collaboration within your team, keeping everyone aligned and your brand's identity polished and cohesive.`    
  },
  {
    id: '3',
    name: 'User Testing and Iteration',
    description:
    `I'll initiate our journey to excellence by subjecting our prototypes to rigorous usability testing, gathering valuable feedback to refine our designs. Diving deep into this feedback, I'll identify and swiftly address any recurring issues, ensuring our solutions are not only innovative but also user-centric. With an iterative approach, I'll seamlessly integrate this feedback, enhancing our designs with precision and expertise.

Collaboration is key in bringing these designs to life. I'll work closely with your development team, bridging the gap between design and technology to ensure our visions are flawlessly executed. But our journey doesn't end at launch. I'm committed to continual improvement, keeping an eagle eye on the product's performance and user feedback, making iterative enhancements to ensure it not only meets but exceeds user expectations and business goals.`
  },

];
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 fade-up">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">My Process</h2>
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <dl
          class="-mt-3"
          x-data="{ selected: '0', toggle(value) { this.selected = (this.selected === value) ? null : value } }"
        >
          {
            features.map((feature, id) => (
              <div
                class="rounded-3xl px-4 transition"
                x-data={`{ id: ${id}, get isOpen() { if (this.id == this.selected) return (true) ; else return this.id === this.selected; }, get isNextOpen() { return (this.id + 1) === this.selected } } `}
                x-bind:class="{ 'bg-primary-400/10 dark:bg-primary-400/10': isOpen }"
              >
                <dt
                  class="border-b text-lg transition"
                  x-cloak
                  x-bind:class="{ 'border-transparent': isOpen || isNextOpen, 'border-primary-300/10 dark:border-primary-300/10': !(isOpen || isNextOpen) }"
                >
                  <button
                    type="button"
                    class="group block w-full py-6 text-left transition focus-visible:outline-none"
                    aria-controls={feature.id}
                    x-on:click="toggle(id)"
                    aria-expanded="true"
                    x-bind:aria-expanded="isOpen.toString()"
                  >
                    <div class="group-focus-visible:outline-primary-200 dark:group-focus-visible:outline-primary-200 flex items-center justify-between rounded-3xl group-focus-visible:outline group-focus-visible:outline-2 group-focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
                      <span class="whitespace-nowrap font-medium">{feature.name}</span>
                      <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
                        <svg
                          class="text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-400 h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform transition duration-200 ease-in-out"
                          x-bind:class="{ '-rotate-180': isOpen, 'rotate-0': !isOpen }"
                          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                          fill="currentColor"
                          aria-hidden="true"
                        >
                          <path d="M11.9997 13.1714L16.9495 8.22168L18.3637 9.63589L11.9997 15.9999L5.63574 9.63589L7.04996 8.22168L11.9997 13.1714Z" />
                        </svg>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </button>
                </dt>
                <dd class="pb-6 pr-6" id={feature.id} x-show="isOpen || id === '1'">
                  <p class="text-primary-200/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base">
                    {feature.description}
                  </p>
                </dd>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
